d to anyone who was offended by a segment of the glamorous opening ceremony that appeared to parodyLeonardo da Vinci's \\\"The Last Supper\\\" painting.\", \"from\": 3866, \"to\": 4052, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3866, \"end\": 3880, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Da Vinci's painting depicts the moment whenJesus Christdeclared that an apostle would betray him.\", \"from\": 4054, \"to\": 4151, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4054, \"end\": 4062, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.986219893642458e-35, \"text\": \"Da Vinci\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The rendition during Friday's ceremony featured DJ and lesbian activist Barbara Butch - an LGBTQ+ icon - flanked by drag artists and dancers.\", \"from\": 4152, \"to\": 4293, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4207, \"end\": 4214, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lesbian\", \"score\": 0.9354695309155564, \"rank\": 0.06898100556391955, \"text\": \"lesbian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lesbian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lesbian\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Religious conservatives from around the world decried the segment, with the French Catholic Church's conference of bishops deploring \\\"scenes of derision\\\" that they said made a mockery of Christianity - a sentiment echoed by Russian Foreign Ministry spokesperson Maria Zakharova.\", \"from\": 4295, \"to\": 4573, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4371, \"end\": 4393, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church_in_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French Catholic Church\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church_in_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church_in_France\"}, {\"begin\": 4378, \"end\": 4393, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 0.9999999999758984, \"rank\": 1.027678691860094e-11, \"text\": \"Catholic Church\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}, {\"begin\": 4482, \"end\": 4494, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9834130679758764, \"rank\": 0.016866690154691038, \"text\": \"Christianity\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}, {\"begin\": 4519, \"end\": 4543, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ministry_of_Foreign_Affairs_(Russia)\", \"score\": 0.999999999875854, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Russian Foreign Ministry\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ministry_of_Foreign_Affairs_(Russia)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ministry_of_Foreign_Affairs_(Russia)\"}, {\"begin\": 4557, \"end\": 4572, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maria_Zakharova\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Maria Zakharova\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maria_Zakharova\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maria_Zakharova\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Anglican Communion in Egypt expressed its \\\"deep regret\\\" on Sunday, saying the ceremony could cause the IOC (International Olympic Committee) to \\\"lose its distinctive sporting identity and its humanitarian message.\\\"\", \"from\": 4575, \"to\": 4793, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4579, \"end\": 4597, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anglican_Communion\", \"score\": 0.999155782765802, \"rank\": 0.0008449305391342007, \"text\": \"Anglican Communion\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anglican_Communion\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anglican_Communion\"}, {\"begin\": 4601, \"end\": 4606, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt\", \"score\": 0.9998975720401629, \"rank\": 0.00010237512410139501, \"text\": \"Egypt\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt\"}, {\"begin\": 4682, \"end\": 4685, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.543966039116291e-17, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 4687, \"end\": 4718, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Clearly there was never an intention to show disrespect to any religious group.\", \"from\": 4795, \"to\": 4875, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"[The opening ceremony] tried to celebrate community tolerance,\\\" the Paris 2024 spokesperson Anne Descamps told a press conference.\", \"from\": 4876, \"to\": 5006, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4944, \"end\": 4954, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.83847997280859e-17, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 4973, \"end\": 4981, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Descamps\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We believe this ambition was achieved.\", \"from\": 5007, \"to\": 5046, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If people have taken any offence we are really sorry.\\\"\", \"from\": 5047, \"to\": 5101, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Controversial media personalityAndrew Tateand his brother Tristan Tate were also among the critics.\", \"from\": 5103, \"to\": 5202, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5161, \"end\": 5168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tristan\", \"score\": 0.9999999971605575, \"rank\": 2.8391918352261818e-09, \"text\": \"Tristan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tristan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tristan\"}, {\"begin\": 5169, \"end\": 5173, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tate\", \"score\": 0.9953825433047654, \"rank\": 0.004638207184861144, \"text\": \"Tate\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tate\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tate\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Sunday, the two stood in front of a church near the French Embassy in Bucharest to protest against the opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 5203, \"to\": 5326, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5276, \"end\": 5285, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bucharest\", \"score\": 0.9999999999977263, \"rank\": 2.4948155579700976e-12, \"text\": \"Bucharest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bucharest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bucharest\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is the Last Supper.\", \"from\": 5328, \"to\": 5353, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is everything holy about Christianity, and we say absolutely nothing about it and say, oh, you cannot even complain.\", \"from\": 5354, \"to\": 5475, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5384, \"end\": 5396, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9834130679758764, \"rank\": 0.016866690154691038, \"text\": \"Christianity\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What are we doing wrong by saying that this is disgusting?\", \"from\": 5476, \"to\": 5534, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is not art,\\\" said Andrew Tate to journalists.\", \"from\": 5535, \"to\": 5585, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5565, \"end\": 5569, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tate\", \"score\": 0.9953825433047654, \"rank\": 0.004638207184861144, \"text\": \"Tate\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tate\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tate\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His brother Tristan Tate added: \\\"What's very important to remember is that the European Union gave \\u20ac100 million for France to do this Olympics.\", \"from\": 5587, \"to\": 5730, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5599, \"end\": 5606, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tristan\", \"score\": 0.9999999971605575, \"rank\": 2.8391918352261818e-09, \"text\": \"Tristan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tristan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tristan\"}, {\"begin\": 5607, \"end\": 5611, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tate\", \"score\": 0.9953825433047654, \"rank\": 0.004638207184861144, \"text\": \"Tate\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tate\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tate\"}, {\"begin\": 5675, \"end\": 5680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999999740794, \"rank\": 1.8820045462640736e-11, \"text\": \"Union\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 5703, \"end\": 5709, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9998231326140096, \"rank\": 0.00017221235719772158, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So they took your money.\", \"from\": 5731, \"to\": 5755, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And they are making fun of Jesus Christ.\", \"from\": 5756, \"to\": 5796, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5783, \"end\": 5795, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999859387305136, \"rank\": 1.4061467344601342e-05, \"text\": \"Jesus Christ\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's our money, you know, that's Romanian taxpayers.\", \"from\": 5797, \"to\": 5849, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5830, \"end\": 5838, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_language\", \"score\": 0.9874512590544751, \"rank\": 0.01270818940471289, \"text\": \"Romanian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are using our money to do this.\\\"\", \"from\": 5850, \"to\": 5887, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Andrew Tate is awaiting trial on charges of human trafficking, rape and forming a criminal gang to sexually exploit women.\", \"from\": 5889, \"to\": 6011, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5896, \"end\": 5900, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tate\", \"score\": 0.9953825433047654, \"rank\": 0.004638207184861144, \"text\": \"Tate\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tate\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tate\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was initially arrested in December 2022 near Bucharest along with his brother Tristan and two Romanian women.\", \"from\": 6013, \"to\": 6125, \"entities\